<HEADLINE>
ON SOCIAL SECURITY, THE GOOD NEWS IS BAD 
</HEADLINE>
  
(Repeating for all needing.)  (The Week in Review)  
 (ART ADV: Graphic is being sent to NYT graphic clients.
Non-subscribers can make individual purchase by calling (888)
603-1036 or (888) 346-9867.) 
(EDITORS: This text is a precede for the graphic cited above. It is
recommended for use only with the graphic.)  
 (bl)  
 c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service    
