   MEANS-COLUMN (Washington) _ Tell me again. Which Dole is running
for president? Bob is all over the place with op-ed pieces calling
on the president to hang tough in Kosovo. While Elizabeth was in
Arizona, echoing his sentiments, she was largely ignored. This
highlights her basic political problem: being taken seriously as a
potential commander-in-chief. By MARIANNE MEANS.
</P>
