<P>
   COMMENT-GENERATION (Undated) _ As a first-generation child of a
Puerto Rican mother and Cuban father, the writer failed to
appreciate the beauty of her culture. Her children will not repeat
the mistake. By Cindy Rodriguez. 830 words.
