<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-04-05 16:18 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6522 &Cx1f; tad-z
u i &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-KOSOVO-JOURNAL-COX     04-05 0865
