<P>
   GLF-MASTERS-NORMAN _ AUGUSTA, Ga. _ Greg Norman's return from
shoulder surgery has been well-documented, but as he heads into one
of his most favorite venues _ Augusta National _ her is a look at
how much the year-long layoff affected his mental approach to the
game. Perhaps the layoff allowed him to exorcise Masters demons.
(Sheeley, Atlanta Journal-Constitution). 25.
</P>
<P>
   GLF-MASTERS-NOTES _ AUGUSTA, Ga. _ Masters notebook. With
Kuchar, Kuehne and Garcia in the field, this could be one of the
strongest amateur fields in Masters history. (Sheeley/Bunn, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution).
</P>
<P>
   GLF-MASTERS-DUVAL _ AUGUSTA, Ga. _ David Duval is the hot topic
of conversation in Augusta, after his fourth win of the year Sunday
in Atlanta. (Bunn) 13''
</P>
<P>
   NFL
</P>
<P>
   FBN-DRAFT-RBACKS _ NFL draft preview: Running backs. Great backs
don't necessarily arrive in the NFL with a flourish, Heisman trophy
winner Ricky Williams acknowledged last week. And many big names
end up as busts. Williams hopes he is an exception. (Pasquarelli,
Atlanta Journal-Constitution) 18.
</P>
