<P>
   TEXLEGIS-AUTOINSURANCE _ AUSTIN, Texas _ Paying for auto
insurance by the mile? That's the proposal by a Fort Worth lawmaker
who says it will help make auto insurance affordable for low-income
families. ``If the state makes drivers buy insurance, we should
give them a way to control insurance costs.'' Burnam plans a
hearing Tuesday on his bill. Several supporter have signed on; none
of them are insurance companies. (Elizondo, Austin
American-Statesman).
