   LOCKERBIE-LIBYA (Utrecht, The Netherlands) _ More than a decade
after Pan Am Flight 103 exploded over Lockerbie, Scotland, killing
270 people, the two Libyan men charged with planting the bomb
arrive in The Netherlands to face trial for the crime. By Marlise
Simons.
</P>
<P>
