of police to search a car after stopping it on suspicion of drugs,
saying that once the car is stopped, police can search any
containers, even if they are not connected to driver. By Linda
Greenhouse.
</P>
<P>
   RWANDA-OUTLOOK (Kigali) _ Five years later, Rwandans are still
playing out a quiet drama _ person by person, village by village _
of regret, forgiveness and, at times, defiance. By Ian Fisher.
1,577 words.
</P>
