hailed as opening a new era in cancer treatment _ can also retard
artery-blocking deposits that cause heart attacks and strokes. By
Richard Saltus. 1000 words.
</P>
<P>
   ELDERLY-DRINKING (Undated) _ One-third of all the elderly -- and
three-quarters of those who drink -- drink too much. Ten percent of
elderly drinkers are doing it on a binge basis. By Larry Tye. 800
words.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; FINANCIAL (f) &LR;
</P>
<P>
   ONLINE-TRADING (Undated) _ Investors funneled stock trades
through the Internet at a record pace in the first quarter; online
trading volumes rose 30 to 35 percent from the fourth quarter. By
Steven Wilmsen. 800 words.
</P>
